data.description: Welcome to 550 N Villa Ct #117, a charming 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo nestled in the desirable Palm Springs community. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the unlimited potential this home has to offer.     Whether you're looking for a move-in ready abode or seeking a project to unleash your creative vision, this condo is the perfect fit for both homeowners and savvy investors alike. Embrace the opportunity to personalize your dream oasis with a full remodel, creating a space that matches your unique style and taste.     Situated on the first floor, this home grants you easy access and the added convenience you crave. The community boasts an array of amenities, including 4 sparkling swimming pools and tennis courts, providing endless opportunities for recreation and relaxation.     Beyond the property's incredible potential lies its unbeatable location. Palm Springs offers a vibrant and thriving lifestyle, with a rich assortment of cultural events, world-class dining, and premier shopping destinations. Immerse yourself in the vibrant energy that this city has to offer, all while basking in the tranquility of your own private retreat.     The seller is motivated and encourages you to make offers, ensuring that this gem can be yours at a great price. Don't miss out on this remarkable opportunity - seize the chance to own a delightful Palm Springs condo with unlimited potential. Fulfill your dreams and make this home your own. Call today to schedule a showing and envision the possibilities that await!
